Name: Nad Paan
Info:
Tucked in a corner of the cozy Karvengar, is Naad, a paan shop complete with a variety of masala paans that blow your mind.
Make sure to have the Dual Chocolate Paan (White & Brown Chocolate), the ayurvedic Sangita Paan, and the unique Ice Paan to experience the innovation of the owner
